Yogurt
Difficulty: 1
Makes: 1 quart

Fage plain yogurt
1 quart whole fat organic milk, unopened

Wash glass containers well. Microwave to sterilize. pour in milk into each container. with a clean spoon, spoon in fage yogurt. Mix, loosely cooverwith lid. put in instand put. put in 3 cups water into the instant pot and set all of the glass containers on a rack in the instant pot. water level should reach 1 inch up the container. press yogurt function, 8 hours.
